title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 57-4.7 - Exemption
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 57-4.7 - Exemption

State Regulations

An institution that offers a registered program leading
to certification pursuant to section
52.21
of this Title, shall not be
required to pay a fee for approval under this section. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8
§§
57-4.7

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
